@startuml
title Viaverse AI Assistant / Human Escalation — Sequence Diagram

actor User
participant "Client" as Client
participant "API Gateway / BFF" as BFF
participant "ai-assistant-service" as AI
participant "policy/privacy guard" as Policy
database "Knowledge Base / Vector Index" as KB
participant "LLM Adapter" as LLM
participant "support-service" as Support
queue "Outbox / Kafka" as Kafka

User -> Client : ask AI
Client -> BFF : POST /ai/ask
BFF -> AI : ask(command)
AI -> Policy : redact + authorize context
AI -> KB : retrieve relevant docs
AI -> LLM : generate with guarded prompt
LLM --> AI : model response
AI -> Policy : output safety check
AI ..> Support : create ticket if uncertain/risky
AI -> Kafka : AiAsked / AiAnswered / AiEscalated
AI --> BFF : answer or escalation status
BFF --> Client : render response

note bottom
ai-assistant-service owns prompt assembly, redaction,
tool boundaries, model call, output checks and escalation decision.
end note
@enduml
